{"word":"G2726 - κατήφεια - katḗpheia - kat-ay'-fi-ah - Heaviness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατήφεια</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>katḗpheia"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kat-ay'-fi-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heaviness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சஞ்சலம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a downcast dejection, gloom"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and perhaps a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a> (meaning <i>downcast</i> in look); <i>demureness</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>sadness:</i> - heaviness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}